mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"f78cbdd635f11672643a64883a33dd7bd4fa33df","tid":773471,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"有被告與受害人在公眾地方手拖手的照片<br />\n<br />\n一定係畀帽人帶/ 貪慕虛榮/<br />\n如果唔係點會咁激動呀 <br />\n臭鴨抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a97e2e89c36e3afd6bd8cc5245ccbf6a87922a7","tid":773471,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"好人好者點會搞gay"}]}